This paper deals with automatic quality estimation of ASR hypotheses and unsupervised adaptation of a deep neural network. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Sound and Music Computing (cs.SD), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Speech Processing (cs.SI).
